dct_title_s: Venetiarum amplissima & maritima urbs : cum multis circumiacentibus insulis
dct_description_sm: Map of Venice; relief shown pictorially. Appears in Münster's Cosmographia, 1572. Pages 218-219 from: Cosmographiae universalis lib. VI / Sebastian Münster. Basiliae : ex officina Henricpetrina, 1572. Latin text and page nos. on verso : Civitas Venetorum ... 217, 220.
